## Image_Processing

The package "image_processing-test" is used to:

-   Processing:

    -   Histogram matching;
    -   Structural similarity;
    -   Resize image;

-   Utils:
    -   Read image;
    -   Save image;
    -   Plot image;
    -   Plot result;
    -   Plot Histogram;

